parameters: Sorry about that, I should have warned you beforehand.
ActorMari
I... I... I can talk again!  What was that???
Welcome to Mount Spection.  It's a beautiful place to
go to be alone for quiet contemplation.  Inside the
mountain, it is impossible to write or speak in any
known language.\n<?> \C[21]
ActorMari
That literally makes no sense... How?
Felipe helped me set that up.  The specifics of how
aren't important, at least not yet.\n<?> \C[21]
ActorMari
Wait, I remember you... We met back on that
tower back in the second chapter!  And your
voice... You were on the loudspeaker at the
train station at the mall!
ActorMari
Your name was something interesting-
wasn't it Harris or something?
You're pretty close- the name I gave you was Ferris.
Not that it matters, lol.\n<Harris or something> \C[21]
ActorMari
What do you mean "the name you gave me"?
Is that not your real name?
All in due time.  You've had to go though a lot to get
here, but you aren't done yet.  You were given a quest
to complete, right? \n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
ActorMari
Oh yeah, that's right!  It feels like it's
been a whole year since that happened.
I'm supposed to go meet someone at the top
of the mountain!  The C.U.L.T told me so!
Oh come on!  Not THOSE guys again.  I told the original
mall owners a few too many things and things got all
out of hand.  I just needed them to monitor the mall's
power source, not go all crazy for unlimited power! \n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
And they ended up blowing up all of time and space a
couple dozen times before you were able to stop them...
\n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
ActorMari
Wait, you know about that?
I thought I reset that timeline?
I set up the wormhole for them, you don't think I'd be
able to bend time a bit too?
\n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
ActorMari
Valid.
ActorMari
Hang on, you set up the power source, you
started the C.U.L.T, and you can bend
time... doesn't that make YOU the
Enlightening One?
ActorMari
That must be your real name then!
Nah, they made that up.  I think they just misheard me
saying something about lightning and got confused.  It
doesn't matter, the point is that you're here now,
and it's my time to shine!\n<"The Enlightening One"> \C[21]
Linus already got his turn, even though he basically
outsourced all of his puzzles to random people around
his archipelago.  \n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
But I'm going to do this right- I've been waiting a
long time to give you some fun puzzles!
\n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
So much so that I've stretched the definition of
"just ten puzzles" that Felipe tasked me with.
\n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
Inside of these caves, you'll find nine interwoven
puzzles, followed by a tenth master puzzle, just like
you've done the past five times.  Just follow the gems-
it will all make sense in time.  \n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
Start with these \C[21]Citrines\C[0], follow those to get a
tutorial for the other puzzles.
\n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
Anyways, I'll see you at the top!  \n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
Happy puzzling! \n<"Ferris"> \C[21]
ActorMari
Hmm, Lightning One..
